<HEAD>Eds: LEADS with 13 grafs to UPDATE with justice minister's comments
from Washington. Pick up 11th pvs, `A Bogota ...' Minor editing to TRIM</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By KEVIN NOBLET</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>BOGOTA, Colombia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
